[quote=“SilentCJ, post:4, topic:251404”]Little tip.
You have to make every single detail separately if you want it to actually look good, for example, the neck has to be a complete different shape, it is a semi cylinder, and each fret marker has to be made individually, and all the pickups, and the tuning keys etc.

Yeh, and get your own ideas lol, i made a guitar because i play it, and have done for over 2 years.
And i looove it.

Go make some cars or some shit.[/quote]

CJ, you know I <3… but you can’t deny him the right to make a guitar. :s Atleast it’s a different style, right?
I mean, maybe he like guitars too?
